breadCrumbs.text: Confirm if you need a contracted out service or supply of resource.

title: Confirm if you need a contracted out service or a supply of resource
subtitle: As the buyer,  you are the supplier’s client when buying a supply of resource  (people to do the work).
SUBTITLE_1: This means that you’re responsible for deciding if the off-payroll working rules  (IR35) apply to them.  You must meet your legal obligations where they do.
subtitle1: Choose whether you need a contracted out service or a supply of resource.
subtitle2: information about your organisation and the problem you want to solve
subtitle3: anything else you think would be useful for them to know
filedesc: you can upload multiple files, each no larger than 300mb, to a total of 1GB. Acceptable file formats: csv, doc, docx, jpg, jpeg, kml, ods, odt, pdf, png, ppt, pptx, rdf, rtf, txt, xls, xlsx, xml, zip
subtitle4: Use the same link (above) to upload any other supporting documents (optional).
